{"article_id":"iOMYLsNFqe4IBlo9","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Former Virginia governor Robert McDonnell and his wife were indicted on Tuesday by a federal grand jury","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"and charged with accepting bribes in the form of money and gifts from the chief executive of a dietary supplements maker .","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"An indictment with 14 counts was filed in U.S. District Court for the Eastern District of Virginia against McDonnell ,","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"who is only 10 days out of office ,","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"and his wife , Maureen .","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"Court appearances for the couple were set for Friday in Richmond .","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"They accepted gifts from the head of supplements-maker Star Scientific Inc","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"including cash , golf fees and clothing","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"and in exchange arranged for company executives to meet government officials","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"who could help their business ,","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"the indictment alleges .","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"The McDonnells , both 59 years old , believe","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"they have done nothing illegal","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"and plan to fight the charges in court ,","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"they said in separate statements through their lawyers .","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"`` We did not violate the law ,","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"and I will use every available resource and advocate","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"I have","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"for as long as it takes","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"to fight these false allegations , ''","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"Robert McDonnell said in his statement .","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"If convicted ,","depth":4},{"id":22,"text":"the McDonnells could face decades in prison and fines","depth":5},{"id":23,"text":"totaling well over $ 1 million .","depth":5},{"id":24,"text":"McDonnell , a Republican , said","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"in July","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"he had repaid $ 120,000 in loans from Jonnie Williams , a major campaign donor and the founder of Star Scientific .","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"He also apologized for the embarrassment","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"the gifts and loans to him and his family had caused Virginia .","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"McDonnell had acknowledged","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"that he and his family received more than $ 160,000 in gifts and loans from Williams .","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"The gifts from Williams ranged from a $ 6,500 Rolex watch for McDonnell , to wedding and engagement presents and money for his daughters , and a $ 15,000 shopping spree for first lady Maureen McDonnell .","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"Attorney Abbe David Lowell ,","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"who represents Star Scientific ,","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"said","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"the company is cooperating with authorities .","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"The relationship started","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"with McDonnell 's staff asking Williams","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"if McDonnell could use his jet aircraft during the 2009 gubernatorial campaign ,","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"said prosecutors ,","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"who referred to Williams only as JW .","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"But","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"after McDonnell won the election ,","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"the relationship grew ,","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"according to the indictment .","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"Maureen McDonnell tried to have Williams pay for an Oscar de la Renta dress","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"she could wear to the inauguration ,","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"and clashed with McDonnell 's staff","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"who dissuaded her from accepting the dress .","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"In an email , Maureen wrote to McDonnell aides :","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"`` I need to talk to you about Inaugural clothing budget .","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"I need answers","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"and Bob is screaming about the thousands","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"I 'm charging up in credit card debt . ''","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"`` We are broke ,","depth":13},{"id":55,"text":"have an unconscionable amount in credit card debt already ,","depth":13},{"id":56,"text":"and this Inaugural is killing us ! ! ''","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"Maureen McDonnell wrote ,","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"according to the indictment .","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"While she was forced to decline that offer ,","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"prosecutors said","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"she soon asked again for help","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"in shopping for designer clothes .","depth":13},{"id":63,"text":"In April 2011 , Williams took Maureen to Oscar de la Renta , Louis Vuitton and Bergdorf Goodman in New York ,","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"racking up nearly $ 20,000 in bills","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"shopping for her daughter 's wedding and other parties ,","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"prosecutors said .","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"Williams later provided many other favors ,","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"including a $ 50,000 loan , a $ 15,000 `` gift ''","depth":13},{"id":69,"text":"to cover wedding expenses ,","depth":13},{"id":70,"text":"and the Rolex watch","depth":13},{"id":71,"text":"engraved with `` 71st Governor of Virginia '' on the back ,","depth":13},{"id":72,"text":"they said .","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"In exchange ,","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"the Justice Department said ,","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"McDonnell introduced the company to Virginia health officials","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"and promoted Star 's products","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"including to Virginia universities","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"which it suggested","depth":13},{"id":79,"text":"conduct related studies .","depth":13},{"id":80,"text":"Current Gov . Terry McAuliffe , a Democrat , issued a statement","depth":7},{"id":81,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"he was troubled by the charges and `` the message","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"that this period in our history sends","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"about how government in this Commonwealth is run . ''","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"On the day","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"he was inaugurated as governor , Jan. 11 , McAuliffe issued an executive order","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"imposing a $ 100 limit on any gifts","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"that he , his family , or members of his administration may receive .","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"The order also provides for an ethics commission","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"to enforce the new standards on members of the executive branch ,","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"and to answer questions from employees .","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"Larry Sabato , director of the Center for Politics at the University of Virginia , suggested","depth":4},{"id":93,"text":"that the disclosures in the indictment set a new standard for misbehavior .","depth":4},{"id":94,"text":"Get the Monitor Stories","depth":5},{"id":95,"text":"you care about","depth":5},{"id":96,"text":"delivered to your inbox .","depth":4},{"id":97,"text":"By signing up ,","depth":4},{"id":98,"text":"you agree to our Privacy Policy","depth":4},{"id":99,"text":"`` I 'm not going to say","depth":6},{"id":100,"text":"the state has n't had corrupt officials ,","depth":6},{"id":101,"text":"but they have been relatively few","depth":6},{"id":102,"text":"- and none at the level of Governor and First Lady , ''","depth":6},{"id":103,"text":"Sabato said .","depth":4},{"id":104,"text":"`` It 's a real shock to those of us","depth":5},{"id":105,"text":"who have lived in the state all our lives","depth":6},{"id":106,"text":"and know the culture , ''","depth":6},{"id":107,"text":"he said .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":215,"left":201,"right":214,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":201,"left":